values: Please comment if you'd like to be added. Let me know who you are or where I know you from when you comment. NOTE #1: I'm happy with my friends list as it is now, however I would probably still add new folks as long as I 'know' them from other places; forums and the like, or friends of people already on my friends list so that I have some idea who's reading my personal friends locked entries. That being said, if we have enough interests in common, I'll probably add you. I post a lot about my personal life, and therefore I don't add any and everyone. I'm sorry. NOTE #2: Please don't add me if you don't intend to comment on my journal or if you don't post entries in yours. NOTE #3: Comments are now screened. (1/10/10) Also, please feel free to watch my icon journal. Those entries are always public.
